OL,3,C#10 million government funding
OL,4,Cconfirmed for Scottish Borders
OL,6,FScotland's Deputy First Minister has
OL,7,Fannounced a #10 million cash injection
OL,8,Fto boost visitors and the economy in
OL,9,Fthe Borders.
OL,11,FIn a visit to Melrose, Kate Forbes
OL,12,Fsaid the money would support the River
OL,13,FTweed trail project, a hundred-mile-
OL,14,Flong walking and cycling route
OL,15,Fconnecting Moffat to Berwick-upon-
OL,16,FTweed.
