OL,3,C#10 million government funding
OL,4,Cconfirmed for Scottish Borders
OL,6,F"The River Tweed Trail is the keystone
OL,7,Fproject within the #25 million
OL,8,FDestination Tweed programme and will
OL,9,Fallow people to travel on foot or by
OL,10,Fbike from the source to the sea,
OL,11,Fconnecting communities and attractions
OL,12,Falong the route. It will be one of the
OL,13,Fgreat long-distance routes in the UK.
